# <type>(<scope>): <subject> (50 chars max) / 简要描述（≤50 字）
# |<---- Preferred subject width 50 ---->|
#
# <body>
# |<---- Body / 正文 wrapped at 72 ------>|
#
# <footer>
# Examples / 示例:
#   feat(ui): add bilingual metric chart export / 新增双语指标导出
#   fix(backend): race in experiment status update / 修复状态更新竞态
#   docs(api): update /runs endpoint description / 更新接口文档
#   refactor(db): migrate to UUID primary keys / 主键迁移至 UUID
#
# Types: feat / fix / docs / refactor / test / chore / ci
# 类型：feat 新功能 / fix 修复 / docs 文档 / refactor 重构 / test 测试 / chore 杂项 / ci
#
# Scopes (examples): backend / frontend / db / api / ui / ci
# 范围（示例）：backend / frontend / db / api / ui / ci
